title: TVS rolls out new scooter in Jupiter series: Check features, price, and more
description: TVS Motors has introduced the new Jupiter 110 scooter at Rs 73,700 (ex-showroom). The scooter features a modern design with LED lighting, Bluetooth connectivity, voice assist, and navigation. It is powered by a 113 cc engine, offering a top speed of 82 kmph. It competes with the Honda Activa 6G and Hero Xoom 110.
